      "content": "therapists and support groups... they just talk about \"coping mechanisms.\" they don't actually change the fact that every single second of my life is agony. it feels like everyone is just trying to trick me into staying in a burning building because they're afraid of the smoke. i just want the noise to stop. i want peace.",
